about.summary: Let your Python tests travel through time.

name: freezegun
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.3.8" %}

package:
  name: freezegun
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: freezegun-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/spulec/freezegun/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a95398cd6760996c16414b71aaefa0c45501682ba7fe2ceb1a1ccdb171a4948e

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - six
    - python-dateutil >=1.0,!=2.0

test:
  imports:
    - freezegun

about:
  home: https://github.com/spulec/freezegun
  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: 'Let your Python tests travel through time.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
